platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If youve ever wondered why certain videos on social media look so much better than others, we can explain: Its because the good ones are made with apps like Adobe Premiere Rush. One of our favorite features is one-click auto-duck audio mixing, which does not add quacking noises but rather automatically adjusts the volume of background music during voice-overs.
